Ladies lock up your men; Brooke Logan is coming to Mzansi! Just when South Africans were fixing the country and calling out all cheating men to order, The Bold and the Beautiful actress Katherine Kelly Lang, popularly known as “Brooke” is headed to the country next month. News that the most popular - and most indiscriminately promiscuous face in SABC3’s soapie is making her way to Mzansi later this month broke yesterday. And there is a state of lowkey panic on the social media streets following the announcement, with most ladies thinking she might snatch their men away from them. In the soapie, Brooke has dated her husband’s family members, from cousins to brothers even her husband’s father. Over the years, the character has married, divorced and remarried. Logan is one of the show’s original cast members, creating the role of “Brooke Logan” whose life on the show has been a roller coaster of love since 1987. “Brooke” has emerged as the show's essential heroine, always in mayhem. The Emmy Award-winning soapie is the world’s most dominant daytime soap currently on television and recently celebrated its 31-year milestone on-air. In SA, she will spend her time meeting fans and visiting South Africa’s historic sites. As part of her personal give-back cause, Breakaway from Cancer - she will be competing in the gruesome and challenging Ironman Championships in Port Elizabeth on September 1, 2018.  